  <description><![CDATA[<p>The beautiful sandy beaches of the Adriatic coast are just a few minutes drive away from the Masseria Don Luigi, <strong>a small bed &amp; breakfast hotel of typical Puglian character</strong>. The Pepe family will welcome you to their masseria which dates back to the 1800s, but which now provides elegant rooms decorated with soft colours and antique furniture. The large freeform swimming pool provides a lovely spot in which to relax, as do the gardens planted with prickly pears and ancient olive trees. The little town of Fasano is only 4 km away and the trulli of Alberobello about half an hour's drive.</p>]]></description>
